
Very simple, given a number, find its opposite.
https://www.codewars.com/kata/56dec885c54a926dcd001095

PHP:

function opposite($n) {
 
 return(($n<0)?abs($n):-abs($n));
}

  
function opposite($n) {
  // Your code here
  return( $n <= 0 ? abs($n) : -$n);
  
}

 
C:

float opposite(float num) {
  //processing...
  return(0-num);
}
